titleInfo.title: (HC) Williams v. People of the State of California
titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER signed by Magistrate Judge Dale A. Drozd on 9/2/14 ORDERING that petitioner shall submit, within 30 days from the date of this order, an affidavit in support of a request to proceed in forma pauperis or the appropriate filing fee; petitioners failure to comply with this order will result in dismissal of this action; and the Clerk of the Court is directed to send petitioner a copy of the in forma pauperis form used by this district.(Dillon, M)
